These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, fanta
There 3 different types of food: grapes, peach, lettuce
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, journalist, fisherman
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, gospel, r&b
There are 3 different nationalities: british, japanese, malaysian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, skiing, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is the japanese##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is the fisherman##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is between the malaysian and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the british##1
 5. the journalist is the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is the british##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of house##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the journalist##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | fanta   | juice           |
| Food          | peach       | lettuce    | grapes         |
| Hobby         | traveling    | baking  | dancing        |
| Job           | librarian | journalist   | fisherman      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | r&b    | house       |
| Nationality   | japanese     | british  | malaysian       |
| Sport         | volleyball     | skiing | baseball |

