.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, water
There 3 different types of food: peach, plum, asparagus
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, family
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, gospel
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, brazilian, italian
3 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, tennis, volleyball
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is the brazilian##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person watching family movies##1
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the person who's sport is handball is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 5. the italian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of soul##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person eating peach is the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate   | water    | lemonade         |
| Food          | peach    | plum | asparagus          |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | family  | scientific     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | funk      | soul         |
| Nationality   | italian      | brazilian   | thai    |
| Pet           | fish        | hedgehog      | chinchilla         |
| Sport         | tennis | handball  | volleyball |

