The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, thriller, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, country, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, polish, thai
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, bird, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, cycling
 1. the person eating avocado is the owner of the bird##1
 2. the thai is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the person watching family movies is the person eating orange##1
 4. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the bird##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the polish and the fan of rock##2
 8. the polish is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
11. the polish is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | orange      | avocado      | lemon      |
| Hobby         | board-games   | video-games | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | family | thriller    | scientific          |
| Music-Genre   | country       | funk      | rock          |
| Nationality   | polish    | turkish  | thai      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig   | bird  | fish        |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | rowing   | cycling     |

