 2. the person drinking iced-tea is the spanish##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the fan of reggae is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the fan of reggae is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the coach is the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the person drinking juice is between the coach and the designer##2
10. the spanish is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
