3 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, motorbike
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 3. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is rowing and the fan of folk##2
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
 7. the person driving the tram is between the person eating pumpkin and the person drinking milk##2
 8. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 9. the pilot is on the right of the fan of funk##1
10. the designer is the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
