 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the person driving the trike is between the person drinking soy-milk and the french##2
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the bike##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
11. the person driving the bike is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate      |
| Hobby         | baking     | gardening     | magic-tricks  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | mystery  | thriller |
| Nationality   | indian  | nigerian     | french |
| Pet           | goldfish        | cat | pony     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | skiing | parkour   |
| Transport     | airplane        | trike        | bike   |

