5. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
7. the accountant is the person eating peas##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
9. the indian is between the person eating peas and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
